{"tid":2364561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人玩過Beholder？","createTime":"2021-01-13T05:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T11:55:17.000Z","uid":363330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de060fa085c2811436843277d05c956f855b1a24","tid":2364561,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"忍唔住課金買咗完整版<br />\n<br />\n玩家扮演一個大廈管理員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以喺每一間房度裝cam 發現住客有咩&ldquo;違法行為&rdquo;就可以向政府報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後好快就有國安嚟搭走條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔舉報就冇錢畀生活費<br />\n<br />\n就算個住客本身冇嘢 但你可以潛入去房放啲&ldquo;違法物品&rdquo;去報國安拉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間會遇到有抵抗勢力 你可以揀暗中幫佢定報國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中有段好難頂 有架大內宣車停喺門口<br />\n不斷播 &ldquo;你們生活在全世界都最的國家&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國安法只係針對小撮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PujwGre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPujwGre.jpg&h=fa2a2a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔准過洋節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vt1i5S6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVt1i5S6.jpg&h=d2889e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色鴨仔係違禁品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />酒吧唔畀營業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJA0zMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJA0zMC.jpg&h=d20b749c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔畀嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deqG3E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeqG3E9.jpg&h=1ecc2b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實同遊戲我就嚟分唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986ce1b20bfe95853a8ed4e15a30d6de17ecaf24","tid":2364561,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}